{"tid":564904,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史高斯憶述復出：因為普巴唔得！","createTime":"2018-02-18T12:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T13:08:52.000Z","uid":4661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee36ab36152f0473d1e83affcdebd90379c01c3","tid":564904,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/2326372.main_image.jpg?w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2F2326372.main_image.jpg%3Fw%3D960&h=1d2a3e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=wKGJgGynjm6lP3PkoXFXv10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7efbcbc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯名宿史高斯最近自爆當年退役6個月後突然復出的背後原因。<br />\n<br />\n史高斯（Paul Scholes）在2010/11球季後退役，卻於6個月後突然復出，他透露因為那時當上曼聯預備組助教，每天跟保羅普巴、連格這些好球員一起操練，在狀態回升下，雄心也回來，而且當時正值球隊用人之際。<br />\n<br />\n「球隊有很多傷兵，沒有中場中球員可用，對布力般流浪時要用上菲爾鍾斯及法比奧達施華。當時普巴以為自己有機會，卻未能踢出表現，所以我有復出的念頭。」史高斯表示。<br />\n<br />\n時任領隊費格遜得知愛徒的想法，立即答應，而且一直保持秘密，直至在作客同市宿敵曼城的英足盃第3圈賽事，讓他擔任後備。43歲的史高斯說：「我要去買球鞋！因為我沒有了贊助，家裡沒有球鞋！」"},{"pid":"f39f5433f597a8e44db92528753a34c1112846a1","tid":564904,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30720bf20514ff3c61afce2529538e14482ad93","tid":564904,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39f5433f597a8e44db92528753a34c1112846a1","tid":564904,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"史高斯依加復出都勁過死黑鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f661dd5abb1d53d049ad448779c5bf338ba1ddb0","tid":564904,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30720bf20514ff3c61afce2529538e14482ad93","tid":564904,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39f5433f597a8e44db92528753a34c1112846a1","tid":564904,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"史高斯依加復出都勁過死黑鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"而家都勁過"}]}